Mode (Magic Number) = 2(DMG + BaneDMG) + DMG Bonus<br>
Maximim = ((Weapon Skill + Strength)/100)*(DMG+ BaneDMG) + DMG Bonus<br>
<br>
The DMG Bonus itself is (Level-25)/3 for 1 Handed Weapons.<br>
<br>
For 2 Handed Weapons, I know of no formula to calculate it ahead of time,  Instead, I've had to look in shops and at other peoples weapons to see what the Damage Bonus is on 2H weapons of various delays for me (at 5<!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> .<br>
<br>
